{"build_type":"library","description":"Whole-universe per-function compile via as-completed fan-out. Body is one as-completed launch: assessor produce-compile-worklist-feeding-collector enumerates source packages and emits each function as a self-contained JSON work item; worker compile-one-function-from-work-item compiles one function into objdir in its own small reclaimed arena. Returns the orchestrator's {completed:N}. Called as a normal function (the launch lowering returns), replacing the one-worker whole-library compile that ballooned to ~1.24GB.","module_name":"compile-universe-via-fanout","package_name":"compile-universe-via-fanout","function_definitions":{"compile-universe-via-fanout":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"launch_worker_binary","target_binary":"compile-one-function-from-work-item","assessor_binary":"produce-compile-worklist-feeding-collector","cycle_type":"as-completed"}]}}}